---
title: Application lifecycle
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Preparing

    Preparing --> Applied: application submitted
    Preparing --> Withdrawn: candidate stops preparation

    Applied --> RecruiterContact: recruiter responds
    Applied --> Rejected: application declined
    Applied --> Withdrawn: candidate withdraws

    RecruiterContact --> TechnicalInterview: technical stage scheduled
    RecruiterContact --> Rejected: process ends
    RecruiterContact --> Withdrawn: candidate withdraws

    TechnicalInterview --> FinalInterview: advances
    TechnicalInterview --> Rejected: process ends
    TechnicalInterview --> Withdrawn: candidate withdraws

    FinalInterview --> Offer: offer received
    FinalInterview --> Rejected: process ends
    FinalInterview --> Withdrawn: candidate withdraws

    Offer --> Archived: outcome recorded
    Rejected --> Archived: outcome recorded
    Withdrawn --> Archived: outcome recorded

    Archived --> [*]

    note right of Preparing
        current status is a read model.
        Every change appends an immutable
        ApplicationTransition in the same transaction.
    end note
